generateTerrain() - Method in class terrain.model.HeightMap
Provided that all details in this HeightMap are set and amenable to terrain generation, this method will fill in the height map data for this HeightMap according to the diamond-square algorithm using the predetermined HeightShifter for this HeightMap.
getGrid() - Method in class terrain.model.HeightMap
Retrieves a two-dimensional grid of values for the height map.
getHeight() - Method in class terrain.model.HeightMap
Retrieves the number of rows in this HeightMap.
getHeightAt(int, int) - Method in class terrain.model.HeightMap
Retrieves an individual height value at a specified position within this HeightMap.
getMaxHeight() - Method in class terrain.model.HeightMap
Retrieves the global maximum height from this HeightMap.
getMinHeight() - Method in class terrain.model.HeightMap
Retrieves the global minimum height from this HeightMap.
getWidth() - Method in class terrain.model.HeightMap
Retrieves the number of columns in this HeightMap.
